content: Vanesse Token or VNES is a token where holders can participate in real estate, car rental, online shopping, concerts, and many more. We are a team crypto enthusiast with business partners spread out in South Korea. Our goal is to create a network of services that one can avail of using a digital currency such as Vanesse Token. Currently, the services are only available in South Korea but we plan to expand our network of services as soon as we're successful in establishing the partnerships and the operations here in South Korea. You can visit our website at https://vanesse.io and although most are written in Korean, we will definitely have a purely English version to cater to the International community. Please join our social media channels to know more about our project.
